---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Return & Refund Policy | Dapper Doxie"
  description="Return and refund policy for Dapper Doxie puppy placements, including health-related refund conditions and claim steps."
  keywords="Dachshund refund policy, puppy return policy, Dapper Doxie policy"
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Return & Refund Policy"
    subtitle="Clear terms for cancellations, health-related returns, and approved refunds"
    breadcrumbs={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Return & Refund Policy' }
    ]}
  />

  <section class="refund-page">
    <div class="refund-container">
      <article class="refund-card">
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 16, 2026</p>
        <p>
          At Dapper Doxie, we are committed to fair and transparent placement policies. This page explains
          when returns and refunds may apply.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Reservation and Deposit Terms</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>A puppy is considered reserved only after payment is confirmed.</li>
          <li>Deposits used to hold a puppy are non-refundable if the buyer changes their mind.</li>
          <li>If Dapper Doxie cannot complete the placement, the paid amount is fully refunded.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Veterinary Check Requirement</h2>
        <p>
          The buyer must complete a licensed veterinary exam within seven (7) days of receiving the puppy and
          provide records if concerns are identified.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Health-Related Refund Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          A full refund may be approved if a licensed veterinarian confirms a serious congenital defect or qualifying
          pre-existing illness within the required reporting window, and the puppy is safely returned.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Communicable Illness Window</h2>
        <p>
          If a communicable illness is diagnosed within fourteen (14) days of arrival and documented by a licensed
          veterinarian, a full refund may be issued upon return and record review.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Transportation Fees</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Approved health-related refunds include documented transportation costs when applicable.</li>
          <li>If a buyer cancels for non-health reasons, transportation and handling fees are non-refundable.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Buyer remorse or household preference changes after reservation.</li>
          <li>Failure to follow veterinary care instructions or maintain basic puppy welfare standards.</li>
          <li>Minor, non-medical preferences (size expectation, ear set, coat shade, etc.).</li>
          <li>Health concerns reported outside policy timelines without supporting records.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Return Request Process</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:info@dapperdoxie.com">info@dapperdoxie.com</a>.</li>
          <li>Provide veterinary records, diagnosis notes, and timeline details.</li>
          <li>Wait for written return authorization before arranging transport.</li>
          <li>After review and approved return, refund processing typically completes within 5-10 business days.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>8. Replacement Option</h2>
        <p>
          In some approved cases, buyers may choose a replacement puppy of equal value instead of a refund, subject
          to availability.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Policy questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:info@dapperdoxie.com">info@dapperdoxie.com</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .refund-page {
    background: #F7FAF7;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-family, 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif);
  }

  .refund-container {
    max-width: 940px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .refund-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .last-updated {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #7a6b5e;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .refund-card h2 {
    margin: 1.2rem 0 0.55rem;
    color: #143521;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .refund-card p,
  .refund-card li {
    margin: 0;
    color: #585858;
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  .refund-card ul,
  .refund-card ol {
    margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .refund-card a {
    color: #1F5132;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .refund-page {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .refund-card {
      padding: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
